1
00:00:00,160 --> 00:00:05,000
As you know, due to her condition, there
are lifelong medications she must take.

2
00:00:05,520 --> 00:00:06,616
This is a matter of life and death.

3
00:00:06,640 --> 00:00:09,080
Her diet also needs strict attention.

4
00:00:09,720 --> 00:00:12,120
I'm fine, there's nothing wrong with me.

5
00:00:13,800 --> 00:00:16,240
It was just a minor fainting spell anyway.

6
00:00:16,680 --> 00:00:18,000
You've completely exaggerated it.

7
00:00:18,360 --> 00:00:21,440
Hospitals and all. I should get up now.

8
00:00:22,120 --> 00:00:24,200
You are the reason for
what Mercan is going through!

9
00:00:25,040 --> 00:00:27,320
If you truly loved Mercan,
you would stay away from her.

10
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:30,240
You'd protect her from
your family's wickedness too.

11
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,160
You know I'm right, too.

12
00:00:33,400 --> 00:00:35,296
If Mercan is in this
state, it's because of you.

13
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:38,200
Don't try to ease your conscience
by blaming it all on your father.

14
00:00:39,120 --> 00:00:40,520
You are Eylül's killer.

15
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:42,640
Ateş knows this too.

16
00:00:43,240 --> 00:00:45,600
If you loved him, you
would stay away from him.

17
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,960
I won't stop until Ateş
separates from Mercan!

18
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:52,400
Seeing them together is worse than death!

19
00:00:52,480 --> 00:00:54,120
Aslı, for God's sake, stop now!

20
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:57,616
I'm tired of beating him, but
he's not tired of being beaten.

21
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,640
Ateş.

22
00:00:59,120 --> 00:01:01,280
Please, let's not have any tension. Please.

23
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:03,280
I'm tired of talking about the same things.

24
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:07,000
You're ruining your own life too.

25
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:10,080
Forget me and go your own way.

26
00:01:10,440 --> 00:01:12,560
My offer to you is valid until I die.

27
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:13,920
Do you know why?

28
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:17,120
Because I know that you and
Ateş cannot have a future.

29
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:24,000
Eylül's shadow will always be between us.

30
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:28,440
Every time you look at me, you'll
remember why your sister died.

31
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:34,720
I wish our paths had never crossed,
so all this pain wouldn't have happened.

32
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,920
I am giving you up for your sake.

33
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,200
I love you so much…

34
